# Keep the build context small and avoid copying stale local artifacts into the
# image. The Dockerfiles install deps + build fresh, so never ship these:
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Secrets never go in an image
.env
.env.local
**/.env

# VCS / tooling / docs not needed at build or runtime
.git
.gitignore
.github
.claude
.agents
docs
**/*.md
.DS_Store
